      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal input uncertainty quantification is not required at Model Risk Level 2. Nominal input values for fluid properties and boundary conditions are documented with sources, but sensitivity analysis is not required at this credibility level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required at Model Risk Level 2. The FDA benchmark dataset provides a single representative pump geometry and experimental conditions sufficient for this credibility level."
    },
    {
